@startuml
actor Client
participant "Assessment Controller" as AssessmentController
participant "Assessment Service" as AssessmentService
participant "Report Controller" as ReportController
participant "Report Service" as ReportService

Client -> AssessmentController: POST /submitEnergyAssessment\nlocation="Leicester no_carbon"
AssessmentController -> AssessmentService: submitAssessment(request)
AssessmentService --> AssessmentController: 201 Created\nassessmentId=ASM-12345678, assessmentStatus=Partial,\ncompletedAt="2026-03-15T10:05:02Z"
AssessmentController --> Client: Partial assessment response

Client -> ReportController: POST /generateSustainabilityReport\n{assessmentId:"ASM-12345678", assessmentStatus:"Partial", completedAt:"2026-03-15T10:05:02Z"}
ReportController -> ReportService: generateReport(request)
ReportService -> AssessmentService: getStoredAssessment("ASM-12345678")
AssessmentService --> ReportService: Stored assessment with fallback CO2 estimate
ReportService --> ReportController: 201 Created\nreportId=RPT-87654321, reportVersion=v1.0
ReportController --> Client: GenerateSustainabilityReportResponse\nwith summaryMetrics, recommendations, dataCompletenessNotes
@enduml
